      "Disparate impact (P(Y=1|unpriv) / P(Y=1|priv)):  0.318\n",
      "  (1.0 = parity; 0.8-1.25 = standard 4/5 rule range)\n",
      "\n",
      "Statistical parity difference (unpriv - priv):    -0.183\n",
      "\n",
      "Equal opportunity difference (TPR_unpriv - TPR_priv): -0.105\n",
