   "source": [
    "## 5. Auditor Self-Assessment: Which Audit Model Should You Use?\n",
    "\n",
    "The choice of audit governance model should not be made implicitly. The questionnaire below scores a system across five dimensions and recommends an audit structure. Run the cell, edit the answers for your specific system, and the recommendation will update.\n",
    "\n",
    "The five dimensions:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **Stakes**- how severe are the consequences of a wrong decision?\n",
    "2. **Public visibility** - does the public have direct access to the system?\n",
    "3. **Regulatory pressure** - is the system subjected to enforceable fairness standards?\n",
    "4. **Internal conflict of interest** - are developers incentivized to underreport unfairness for their own gain?\n",
    "5. **Community input** - do affected communities have a voice in defining acceptable outcomes?\n",
    "\n",
    "Each is scored 0 (low) to 3 (high). The total will lead to an audit governance recommendation."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
